description:
Hey cool spot on Powell Street. First time here last night with a bunch of friends. Address reads 525 Sutter but you actually have to walk around the corner to Powell and you must show ur I.D to the bouncer.  Across from Sir Frances Drake Hotel. 

Once you walk up couple flights of stairs, it's a huge man-cave!!  Lots of arcade games and a full bar. Feels like back in college days again, woohoo! Drinking pitchers of beer, chowing down on bar food: wings, truffle fries / sweet potato fries. The boys taught me how to play shuffle board =}
Pregame here before the clubs!
